%F A002741 Recurrence: a(0) = 0, a(1) = 1, a(2) = -1, a(n) = (n-3)*a(n-1) + 2*(n-2)*a(n-2) + (n-2)*a(n-3).
%F A002741 a(n) + a(n+1) = A000166(n). (End)
